<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>to be able to do</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$contacts = $gdata-&gt;getFeed($contactsQuery);
$total = count($contacts);
</code></pre>

<p>Zend_Gdata_App_Feed needs to be implementing Countable interface. It already implements Iterator and ArrayAccess.</p>

<p>Now the only way is</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$contacts = $gdata-&gt;getFeed($contactsQuery);
$total = $contacts-&gt;count();
</code></pre>

